select `volunteer_id`, `hours` from `habitat_VolunteerHours` where `volunteer_id` in (select `contact_id` from `habitat_FamilyContact` inner join `habitat_Family` on `habitat_FamilyContact`.`family_id` = `habitat_Family`.`id`) and `family_id` = '3'
